import axios from "axios";

module.exports [getUrl, postUrl, putUrl, deleteUrl] = [axios.get('http://localhost:8080/'), axios.post('http://localhost:8080/'), axios.put('http://localhost:8080/'), axios.delete('http://localhost:8080/')];
